{"tid":1881901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟代表與王毅會晤 歐盟代表稱關閉中國邊境、中斷航線等過度反應係不恰當。","createTime":"2020-02-15T22:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:24:15.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a72c5780fa490a5a8516a6826c8a9ad78680b71a","tid":1881901,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508813-20200216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508813-20200216.htm&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=20ffe737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508813-20200216.htm&h=e19e4d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508813-20200216.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外長王毅與歐盟外交與安全政策高級代表博雷利會晤。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》引述博雷利報道，相信中國很快戰勝疫情。歐方已向中方提供了一些援助，願意根據中方需要提供更多防疫醫療物資。報道又引述博雷利表示，關閉邊境、中斷航線等過度反應並不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n王毅重申，不管歐盟身處順境還是逆境，中方始終支持歐盟發展壯大，疫情無國界，中方為阻止疫情向世界傳播做出了努力，願同歐方加強合作，共同應對好人類社會面臨的共同挑戰。"},{"pid":"a91adc9bcd28eac3c603d746907bf6fa1a777229","tid":1881901,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:19:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767904e40dd88a67cb2c843cb46e0d0a3b442bd4","tid":1881901,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d64e9c6a52c89a692e7ab65c265d6a37957cc83","tid":1881901,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歐盟  ：I love 人民幣"},{"pid":"b9fc4b5dec2bce4c854efd1e0021758947f5ec55","tid":1881901,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T22:28:08.000Z","msg":"歐盟=德法揸fit<br />\n奶共奶到咁唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm